

tsc --watch or tsc -w (for single typescript file)


Compiling multiple typescript files
tsc --init
tsc

to exclude some files
1.  open tscconfig.json
2. before the last closing curling brace add exclude
    as "exclude":[
        "something.ts",
        "something2.ts",
        "*.dev.ts",
        "node_modules"// this is defalut
    ]
3. 